data.description:
Immerse yourself in luxury living in this stunning two-story home nestled in a sought-after northwest neighborhood. Tucked away in a tranquil cul-de-sac, this residence boasts a functional loft and a versatile den space, perfect for any purpose you desire. Step outside to your own private oasis featuring a recently added heated pool, surrounded by low-maintenance desert landscaping both front and back.

Benefit from lower power bills with leased solar panels included with the property. Entertain effortlessly in the chic kitchen adorned with quartz countertops, an L-shaped layout offering convenient bar seating, and stainless steel appliances that are yours to keep. Enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping amenities, offering a plethora of options.  Less than 10 minutes per Google maps to Target, Costco, Walmart and other shopping.
